==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhead
<hw>Un*head"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>head</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To take out the head of; <as>as, to <ex>unhead</ex>
a cask</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To decapitate; to behead.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>T. Brown.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unheal</ent>⟦br⟧
